{"title_page": "Romania during World War I", "text_new": "{{Infobox military conflict\n| conflict = Romanian Campaign\n| partof   = the [[Balkans Campaign (World War I)|Balkan]] and [[Eastern Front (World War I)|Eastern Front]] of [[World War I]]\n| image    = Romanian troops at Marasesti in 1917.jpg\n| image_size = 300px\n| caption  = Romanian troops at [[M\u0103r\u0103\u0219e\u0219ti]] battlefield in 1917.\n| date     = August 27, 1916 \u2013 December 1917, November 10\u201311, 1918\n| place    = [[Kingdom of Romania|Romania]]\n| result   = [[Central Powers]] victory\n* [[Armistice of Foc\u0219ani]] (9 December 1917)\n* [[Treaty of Bucharest (1918)|Treaty of Bucharest]] (7 May 1918)\nAllied victory \n* November 1918 \n* [[Treaty of Versailles]], [[Treaty of Saint-Germain-en-Laye (1919)|Treaty of Saint-Germain]], [[Treaty of Neuilly-sur-Seine|Treaty of Neuilly]], [[Treaty of Trianon]]\n| combatant1  = {{flagcountry|German Empire}}<br>{{flagcountry|Austria-Hungary}}<br>{{flagcountry|Kingdom of Bulgaria}}<br>{{flagcountry|Ottoman Empire}}\n| combatant2  = {{flagcountry|Kingdom of Romania}}<br>{{flagcountry|Russian Empire}}\n*[[Romanian Volunteer Corps in Russia|Romanian Corps]]\n{{flagcountry|Kingdom of Serbia}}<ref>[http://www.historia.ro/exclusiv_web/general/articol/voluntari-s-rbi-frontul-rom-nesc-dobrogea Serbian volunteers on the Dobruja Front ('''Romanian''')]</ref><br>''Support:''<br>{{flagcountry|French Third Republic}}\n| commander1  = {{flagicon|German Empire}} [[Erich von Falkenhayn]]<br>{{nowrap|{{flagicon|German Empire}} [[August von Mackensen]]}}<br>{{flagicon|German Empire}} [[Johannes von Eben]]<br>{{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Charles I of Austria|Archduke Karl]]<br>{{nowrap|{{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Arthur Arz von Strau\u00dfenburg|A. A. von Strau\u00dfenburg]]}}<br>{{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Franz Rohr von Denta]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Bulgaria}} [[Stefan Toshev]]<br>{{flagicon|Ottoman Empire}} [[Mustafa Hilmi Pasha]]\n| commander2  = 