ranz Rohr von Denta]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Bulgaria}} [[Stefan Toshev]]<br>{{flagicon|Ottoman Empire}} [[Mustafa Hilmi Pasha]]\n| commander2  = {{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Ferdinand I of Romania|Ferdinand I]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Constantin Prezan]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Alexandru Averescu]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Eremia Grigorescu]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Ioan Culcer]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Mihail Aslan]]<br>{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Vladimir Viktorovich Sakharov|Vladimir Sakharov]]<br>{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Dmitry Shcherbachev]]<br>{{nowrap|{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Andrei Zayonchkovski]]}}<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Serbia}} [[Milenko Mili\u0107evi\u0107]]<br>{{flagicon|French Third Republic}} [[Henri Berthelot]]\n| units1      = {{flagicon|German Empire}} [[9th Army (German Empire)|9th Army]]<br>{{flagicon|German Empire}} [[52nd Corps (German Empire)|Danube Army]]<br>{{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[First Army (Austria-Hungary)|1st Army]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Bulgaria}} [[Third Army (Bulgaria)|3rd Army]]<br>{{flagicon|Ottoman Empire}} [[VI Corps (Ottoman Empire)|VI Corps]]<hr>{{flagicon|Austria-Hungary|naval}} [[Austro-Hungarian Danube Flotilla|Danube Flotilla]]<br>{{flagicon|German Empire|naval}} [[Constantinople Flotilla]]\n| units2      = {{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Romanian Front (Russian Empire)|Romanian Front]]\n*{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[4th Army (Russian Empire)|4th Army]]\n*{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Danube Army (Russian Empire, 1916)|Danube]]/[[6th Army (Russian Empire)|6th Army]]\n*{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[9th Army (Russian Empire)|9th Army]]\n*{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Second Army (Romania)|2nd Army]]\n*{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[First Army (Romania)|1st Army]]\n*{{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[8th Army (Russian Empire)|8th Army]]\n{{flagicon|Kingdom of Romania}} [[Fourth Army (Romania)|4th Army]]<br>{{flagicon|Kingdom of Roma