ell (Ov\u00eddeo TV S.A., Televisi\u00f3 de Catalunya (TVC))\n** ''Clara Campoamor. La mujer olvidada''&nbsp;\u2013 Laura Ma\u00f1\u00e1 (Televisi\u00f3n Espa\u00f1ola (TVE), Distinto Films, Televisi\u00f3 de Catalunya (TVC))\n|}\n\n==Honorary Gaud\u00ed Awards==\n\n* [[Pere Portabella]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:4th Gaudi Awards}}\n[[Category:Catalan cinema]]\n[[Category:Catalan awards]]\n[[Category:Spanish film awards]]\n[[Category:2012 in Spanish cinema]]\n[[Category:2012 in Catalonia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2019}}\nThe 4th Annual Gaud\u00ed Awards, overseen by the Catalan Cinema Academy (''Acad\u00e8mia del Cinema Catal\u00e0'') were held 6 February 2012 at the Arteria Theater Paral\u00b7lel in [[Barcelona]], [[Catalonia]].\n\nWinners are listed first and highlighted in '''boldface'''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.academiadelcinema.cat/en/awards/iv-premis-gaudi.html|title=IV Gaud\u00ed Awards winners|publisher=Catalan Cinema Academy|access-date=2012-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308181321/http://www.academiadelcinema.cat/en/awards/iv-premis-gaudi.html|archive-date=2012-03-08|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vilaweb.cat/noticia/3981160/20120207/mientras-duermes-eva-confirmen-pronostics-sis-cinc-estatuetes-premis-gaudi-respectivament.html| title='Mientras duermes' i 'Eva' confirmen els pron\u00f2stics amb sis i cinc estatuetes dels Premis Gaud\u00ed, respectivament| editor=[[Vilaweb]]|date=7 February 2012|language=Catalan}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.ara.cat/cultura/Mientras-duermes-Eva-reparteixen-Gaudi_0_641336058.html| title='Eva' i 'Mientras duermes' es reparteixen els Gaud\u00ed | date=7 February 2012|publisher=[[Ara (newspaper)|Ara]]|language=Catalan}}</ref>\n{| class=wikitable style=\"width=\"150%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | Best Film in Catalan language \n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | Best Film